zy" title="Biffy Clyro – “从此幸福的神话” | Biffy Clyro逐个轨道" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0tFj_ijJCI8?start=723&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>乐队发布的“庆祝开始”节目中的帖子调侃“在 Biffy X 之前”——暗示他们的第十张专辑即将发行。该乐队的最后一张专辑是 2021 年广受好评的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/biffy-clyro-a-celebration-of-endings-album-review-2725267">The Myth Of The Happily Ever After</a> 》，它是 2020 年《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/biffy-clyro-a-celebration-of-endings-album-review-2725267">A Celebration Of Endings</a> 》的后续专辑和姐妹专辑。</p><p>从那以后的几年里，尼尔一直忙于与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/OCEANSIZE">Oceansize</a>的 Mike Vennart、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slayer">Slayer</a>的 Dave Lombardo 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BITCH-FALCON">Bitch Falcon</a>的 Naomi Macleod 合作的长期悬念的碾核副项目<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/EMPIRE-STATE-BASTARD">Empire State Bastard</a> – 去年发行了首张专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/empire-state-bastard-rivers-of-heresy-review-biffy-clyro-slayer-3490985">Rivers Of Heresy</a> ” 。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/victorious-festival-announces-headliners-for-2024-buy-tickets-3553549">Biffy Clyro 也将成为 8 月份朴茨茅斯胜利音乐节的主角</a>。</p><p>比<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/biffy-clyro-first-three-albums-beggars-london-glasgow-tickets-3599600">菲·克莱罗 (Biffy Clyro) 在伦敦和格拉斯哥的特别演出中完整演奏前三张专辑的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
